{
  "texts": [
    "For this purpose, input texts are fed into the model to acquire output embeddings.",
    "Afterwards, these are pooled in various ways and fed into a final prediction layer, e.g., a linear maximum entropy layer for multiclass classification tasks.",
    "The layers learn to encode different formal and semantic aspects of languages (Tenney et al., 2019).",
    "This can be leveraged by end users who fine-tune the model for specific tasks.",
    "In our approach we combined GBERT with a sliding window, similar to Zehe et al. (2021)."
  ]
}